    "name": "Canopy Predator",
    "prerequisite": "*Verduran Shadow Dedication*; trained in *Athletics*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You are as at home in the treetops as you are beneath their branches. You gain a climb Speed of 15 feet when moving through trees, vines, and other foliage. Whenever you succeed at an Athletics check to Climb a tree or an Acrobatics check to Balance on a branch, you get a critical success instead. You aren\u2019t off-guard while Climbing or Balancing on a tree.",
